Class ParamStore

java.lang.Object
  se.miun.itm.input.model.param.ParamStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
Identifiable
public class ParamStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements Identifiable

a The datastructure that manages all parameter related activities in InPUT. Every design space has a parameter store, to which it outsources its initialization, parameter lookup, and data consistency control. The ParamStore makes sure that the mappings are bound correctly to the parameter definitions, and else report otherwise.

Felix Dobslaw
